{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went and I got the Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took the shoes, and I punched the Russian right in his face.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we ran away because some of the Russian's people were coming to get us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's the only way Dario took me to him, because he had fed me, Dario, because I was much stronger than him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this what happened in the quarantine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody was trying to steal something else from somebody else, a cloth or a-- a hat, or shoes, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So about how long were you in quarantine?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How long would you say, weeks, a month?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took us maybe two weeks, three weeks, something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly everything, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Carol. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us right away to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what we saw on the crematoriums and I was in crematorium three, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] what we saw over there for the first time, was over there four crematories-- I could make the design of it, because I got them in my mind-- was four crematories, four ovens in the crematorium, which every crematorium took about three people in it.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it took about 15 to 20 minutes to burn up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three, the most was three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always, we used to put a woman in the center and two men by the sides, because with the flame, the woman is much fat than the men.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the flames was going to the men's body, and they were burning all the-- all the way at the same time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- the gentlemen, the SS men, they had preventing everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were thinking about everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was everything was working like a watch, like a clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
